---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = 'Privacy Policy';
const description = 'Read our privacy policy to understand how we handle your data at Smart Invite.';
const texts = {};
---
<Layout title={title} description={description} texts={texts}>
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto py-12 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-4">Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how Smart Invite collects, uses, and protects your information when you use our digital invitation services.</p>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>Personal information you provide (such as name, email, event details).</li>
      <li>Usage data (such as device information, IP address, and interaction with our platform).</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>To provide and improve our services.</li>
      <li>To communicate with you about your invitations and account.</li>
      <li>To comply with legal obligations.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">3. Data Sharing and Security</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>We do not sell your personal information to third parties.</li>
      <li>We may share data with trusted partners to operate our service, under strict confidentiality agreements.</li>
      <li>We implement security measures to protect your data.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">4. Your Rights</h2>
    <ul class="list-disc ml-6 mb-4">
      <li>You can request access, correction, or deletion of your personal data.</li>
      <li>Contact us at support@smartinvite.me for any privacy-related requests.</li>
    </ul>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2">5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We encourage you to review it regularly.</p>
    <p class="mt-8">If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:support@smartinvite.me" class="text-blue-600 underline">support@smartinvite.me</a>.</p>
  </main>
</Layout> 